content.detailedDescription: I was driving. observed green oval traveling straight path, it was impossble to not notice this as it was large, green and bright. visible for 4-5 seconds moving much faster than a plane (5x or more a plane at cruise) then blinked out in an instant. this oval came from the north traveling right over niagara falls intl airport and niagara falls airforce base towards the south. i was on williams road, it was parallel. i observed it when it was next to me 90 degrees at about 33 degrees off the ground, green oval. had the apparent size of a full moon. other passenger in the car exclaimed loudly as did i. this wasn't something you'd not notice. no sound. it did not look like a meteor breaking up.No tail. no bright flashes. nothing breaking off it. it was a green perfect cicularly shaped object for the entire time we saw it.. 4-5 seconds. when it looked to be over grand island ny it blnked out. i mean it was there and then it was not there. it did not go behind clouds or below horizon. it simply blinked out. we were both amazed as this was stark, unambiguous. we have no clue what this was. i am 61 years old and i have seen many meteors, shooting stars break up in person and this was not that. i have never observed anything remotely like this. it moved in a straight line, consistent speed and altitude while we observed it. it made no manuevers or displayed any intelligent control. the way it dematerialized was shocking, stark. it did not disappear gradually. the best way i can describe is that it blinked out as if a light blub turned off. it was there and in the smallest possible observable instant it was not there.
content.summary: Green oval niagara falls ny

content.detailedDescription: Every day we observed a stationary star in the south-east above bang phli. while the sky is cloudy. no other stars to trace in the neighbourhood. in fact, my girlfriend attended me on this light. i get my camera and made some photos. then i decided to record it with the camera. pity enough i had no tripod. so, i had to control myself while zooming in, to keep the camera steady. bit by bit i zoomed in, then i saw it more clear. looks there is a dome one it or more domes. looks there is a certain kind of pattern on the surface of the object. i was aware if there was something moving on it. transfer of place on the object. the object was every day on the same spot. once i requested a colleague to look at the sky in the certain direction and he saw the object too. certainly, it is no imagination.
content.summary: The stationary object looked pentagon/ heptagon shaped, when zoomed in, with my sony dsc-hx50. i had no tri-pod.

content.detailedDescription: At the time i would be about 6 or 7 years old. my friends older brother asked me at school if id seen the fairies at night. no i said, he said look up at the sky when its dark. so that night i got up again at about 11pm and sat watching these lights on my window sill. there were several bright orbs hovering in the night sky. id say 4. they were red, green and blue/white colours. i cant say if they changed colour or not. they were rotating about each other and through high clouds that were drifting across the summer night sky. i sat watching them for 20 or 30 minutes, then decided it was time to go back to bed. i remember as clear as yesterday, but have never told anyone before except my friends brother next day at school. i have no idea what these orbs were, but ive never seen anything like them again.
content.summary: Several bright orbs hovering in the night sky. id say 4. they were red, green and blue/white colours.

Just got back from picking my son up, and we both saw an extremely bright light. as it got closer we realized that it was flying low and was not a plane. we thought at first might be a drone but no noise whatsoever. completely silent tiriangle shape with lights, was floating about 500 feet almost directly overhead like nothing we've ever seen. 
+1 561-248-6885
content.summary: Triangle shaped object with lights

content.summary: A round green hovering glow about 11 feet wide

content.detailedDescription: February 23: on delta flight 43 traveling from jfk to atlanta around 6:30 pm i suddenly felt compelled to look out my window for some strange reason almost as if i were prompted... i then noticed a faint object in the distance that i really had to focus on... i waited to see if it was air traffic from another flight, but the object appeared completely different from any airplane, jet, zeppelin, etc. it seemed as if it were a few miles away but strange enough to keep my attention.. it stayed consistent in motion for a few moments, but the longer i focused my attention the more it seemed to change position.. moving left to right, or suddenly blinking in and out view.. very difficult to describe what i saw exactly, but it didn't seem like anything i could really wrap my mind around. i took my iphone out which came out to be pretty lo in quality, but i had my boyfriend enhance the footage by slowing it down/increasing the scale/reducing noise/adding contrast. i have the original footage upon request, but as you can see, the object really emerged once we enhanced the original footage.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Round or cylindrical ojbect hovering a few miles away seen from passenger on airplane above clouds

content.detailedDescription: Had diner at resort went to beachfront parking lot after diner and my wife observed a strange white/blue object below cloud cover it was over cast and raining. i video tape object for 52 sec then got in car went home. i did a 10 zoom of object then panned camera to left hwy 4 and right to the ocean so the experts can determine exact location along with gale each coordinates. the was feb 19 at 7:02 pm. object appeared to be moving but mostly hovering. i don't believe in ufo but none the less this is what i saw and recored. video and google map location provided. feed back welcome.
content.summary: Round blue white object video 52 sec very overcast below cloud cover due to rain

content.detailedDescription:
I run a night vision camera 24/7 pointed up at the sky through my bedroom window facing west. these objects seem to come from afar(up to 9 at one sighting)and very slowly appear closer and closer and spread apart.They are all cylinder shape with a thick black bottom and top.Sometimes two or even three will hook up together side by side.The amazing thing about night vision camera videoing is that although the objects are right there in front of you on the monitor screen--they can't be seen by the human eye. i have read about what is really going on in space when revealed with using night vision.
now--the amazing thing is that in order to zoom in to the object in the video;i had to use my iphone 6 plus;--that when zoomed to as far as i could, you can see in the photo i have how the object turns into a saucer with identical domes on top and bottom of the craft! very interesting. now i am just going to take a wild stab here and suggest that these objects are actually the interior propulsion systems.
mark cerone-videos taken around 3-3-to 3-15-2017
content.summary: These objects were shot from my bedroom window during daytime with a night vision camera running 24/7. they came between 1pm and 5pm starting about 3-3-17. when i try to zoom to max.-they appeared as saucer shape.

content.detailedDescription: On my way to an appointment, traveling south on rt. 301 in waldorf, md approaching the intersection with rt. 5 i saw what was possibly an airplane. it was blue but it did not appear to have all features of an airplane.  it was traveling in the distance from southwest toward northeast in the air at a distance.  it was traveling at the speed that an airplane may travel.  when it got closer it banked to the left, when i was able to make out the diamond shape.  i would guess it was about 20' x 50' in size.  its color/material was a blue-white shimmering metal.  i pulled into the parking lot just past the above mentioned intersection. it had turned and was now behind me, it was traveling west - i was then looking north at it from rt. 301.  when i went to get a camera and binoculars out of my car it was gone.
content.summary: Saw blue object flying in straight path in the air above city in the distance as it came nearer it banked to the left that is when i could see that it was a diamond-shaped object and not a plane.

content.detailedDescription: I was simply video taping, trying to catch someone messing with my windshield while i was in the house.  i wasn't in the car.  had it recording for over 15 minutes.  played the recording back when i got home.  thinking to myself, "well if i didn't catch someone messing with my window, maybe a caught a ufo, ha ha ha" then at the very end of the recording, at the 17:29 mark, right after i start the car, boom, to bright lights go across the sky. one going straight across and a second later, a second one following.  small, white, very bright orb like.  i wanted others opinions.  not my first time, ever , trust me., ever seeing anything.  i've seen much better than that in my life, just never caught anything.
content.summary: At the 17:29 mark is when i noticed the two shooting bright lights, i had my cell phone on my dashboard to try and catch someone messing with my car when i noticed the two orbs of light shoot across

content.detailedDescription:
Filled out with the witness, over the phone at mufon headquarters, by field investigator l. flechtner #18809, on march 21st, 2017.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

my dog started barking and i went outside to my backyard and saw a large silver triangle with bright red lights coming down fast, like it was going to crash. it was coming in nose first and moving back and forth.  it then stopped and hovered over my back yard. i ran inside to get my bright flash light and thought when i went out it would be gone, but it was still there. it was about 200' across. i shined my one million candle watt flashlight at it and it released a cloud that came over me and circled me and then went back into the back of the craft. the bottom of the craft was lit up so bright i just saw noting but bright pulsating red lights. it hovered over my backyard for a few minutes and then just shot up into the sky and disappeared. it came in from the east and finally left toward the west. i heard no sound and felt no other sensations. my dog heard it coming, but i never heard a thing.
i can draw a picture of it.
i don't remember the day, but it was the middle of the week. 
i was in law enforcement and now i am retired from the fire department.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: My dog started barking and i looked outside my backyard and saw a large silver triangle with bright red lights coming down fast like it was going to crash, then it stopped and hovered over my back yard.

content.detailedDescription: I walked out to my car on march 3rd 2017 at around 8p to get my phone charger whe i noticed lights out of the corner of my eye cross the street facing south which is a field filled with cows. it was a clear night and the lights where just there i counted 5 of them thought the neighbors were lighting those sky lanterns that dissolve in the air. i watched for a minute more they didn't move social i went to get my phone to take pictures came back out they still hoovering about 3 minutes had passed i started shaking and getting nervous and video taped the lights and them took pictures and noticed they were getting a little farther away from me and told myself i have to call someone i know, so i called my friend kimmie and asked her to go outside and see if she can see any lights in the sky, by this time i was shaking because the lights weren't moving just hoovering. i decided to take a second video and watched as one light faded off and disappeared in a blink. my friend i called was in montgomery by lake conroe she didn't see any lights that night. i asked the owner of the house can airplanes bye seen from here be seen going to the airport she said no. i knew they weren't airplanes or weather balloons.
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Witnessed lights i sky at night in waller texas on march 3rd 2017

content.detailedDescription:
I was standing outside by back yard and decided to take a few pictures of the sun setting. i took about 10 pictures; but did not notice anything unusual in the view display before taking the photos. it was only when i went back inside and looked at each that i noticed the object at about 10:00 in one of the photos. 

the photo is 181650 and i have included a shot right behind that one181940, another showing a home next door 182417 on the other side of my fence to hopefully give an estimated elevation, and two blowups/ screenshots using my phone i did this morning. 

the sun is casting light directly on the object at an angle it is away from it; which rules out lens flare. the normal flare one would experience when shooting the sun (which would look like a second sun); i aimed it back into to sun.
 
i was using a samsung note 5 cell phone.
content.summary: Unknown object observed near sun disappears after photographed. the object is reflecting sun light.

content.detailedDescription:
Sitting on deck of house under construction having a beer and looking at sky
i saw the light coming across the treetops
helicopter it came in smoothly over trees and descended as if to land, i was angry because i thought some idiot was landing a helicopter in my backyard! 
jumped up and came around the deck to the side where it was coming down. i stayed there observing because i didn't want to approach it while it was landing. i couldn't see what it was because of the light, i assumed it was a searchlight on the front of a helicopter. extremely bright and unusual as it was like the color of light from a full moon. i assumed it was a military helicopter with high tech lighting, west point military academy and stewart airport are nearby. i am in between these two and often see helicopters flying over.
the light was extremely bright and i couldn't see behind it as it was pointed straight at me.
as i waited to ball the pilot out i realized it wasn't making any noise, and it just seemed to be looking back at me.
then i realized i had my phone in my side pocket. i began to reach for it and the object shot straight up like it thought i was reaching for a gun or something.
the speed was incredibly fast and in moments it was so high it looked like a star and kept going until it disappeared before my eyes. i knew it was a ufo at that moment and not a helicopter. and knew no one would believe me. incredible.I never heard a sound from it and it was within 40' of me before it took off. no wind or air displacement was noticeable either.
the two trees it passed seem to have been affected as they are visibly damaged.The weeds grew extremely high ( 6')where the object hovered. 
i can't say i know what it was as the light was so bright, i thought helicopter size but the light could have been the whole thing.
this really happened.
900' elevation on storm king mountain new side
content.summary: Light came along side of mt.At treetops entered my yard and descended as to land thought it was a helicopter then observed me and as i reached for cell phone camera it shot straight up at incredible speed until i could no longer see it

content.detailedDescription: Around 2215 hours from my back porch i saw a bright star i had never seen before in the east sky.  it was bright and then i saw an equally bright triangle shaped object moving towards the star.  it appeared to be in orbit or at least at the top of the atmosphere.   the triangle had to be moving quickly.  it covered five foot of the sky from my view in just a minute.  the star seemed to get brighter and then dimmed.  the star had an odd shape.  it had tree spikes from the top and the what looked like bar under it. then to spikes coming down from the bottom.  after the triangle merged with the star shape, it looked more like a star.  the star then began moving slowing to the south.  i than went to bed after i woke up my wife.  she was not happy.  i have been a deputy sheriff's in tampa fl for twenty year.  i have never seen anything like this before.  we do have mcdill airforce base in tampa.  if it was them, it had to be a major secret?  i have checked tonight, and there is no star where i observed this event.  i tried to take a couple of photos with my wife's cell phone at the end of the event.  i have not checked them.
content.summary: Star like with triangle shape moving into it.

content.detailedDescription: Aprox 9pm last night (3/19/17) i was looking at the stars and some jetliners when i wittnessed a series of star-like objects traversing the sky at extremely high altitudes...In a 15 min period i saw 6 of these objects traveling in various directions...I had an almost identical experience the night before (3/18/17) at aprox the same time...The objects were white, unblinking lights...They traveled at high rates of speed and on 2 occasions the objects vanished suddenly...  i have been seeing strange things in the skys of this town for about 2 years...My wife has also been present on numerous occasions...I am a firm skeptic and i am not in any way assuming that these objects are w/o a doubt extra terrestrial...I am sure, however, that i have seen things that cannot be conventional aircraft...
content.summary: Star-like in appearance, i saw several w/in 15 min

content.detailedDescription: On march 18th 2017 at approximately 8:20 pm, my girlfriend and i decided to go to boston pizza to watch the hockey game.  as we came down truro heights road facing the cobequid bay we saw a bright object that appeared to glow brighter and become larger in size.  it suddenly went dim and could no longer be seen.  we decided to go west toward old barns ns rather than east to the restaurant to see if we could pull over and have a look around to see if we could find it again.  it appeared about 1 km west of its original location over onslow ns and again started small and began to glow brighter and appeared to become larger.  i was able to get a few quick photos of the object.  it remained completely stationary while illuminated both times.  we drove further down the road to the waste treatment facility and observed it once more for a shorter period of time as the vantage point there were several buildings obstructing our view.  we did not see it appear again and decided to go back to town.  it appeared to be no more than 100-200 ft off the ground maybe less.
content.summary: An orb shaped object appeared over onslow ns and began to glow brighter and become larger then disappeared.  approximately 15 seconds later appeared again about 1 km west of original location

content.detailedDescription: I was coming home from work on a december night in 2014. at the end of this one long hilly road, you come to a four way stop. diagonally, there is a large empty field. and beyond that is the base. once i got to the stop sign there was another car in front of me and we simultaneously saw something in the sky and hit the breaks immediately in the middle of the road. there were 12 or more lights lined up in an oval shape larger then a football field. it could have been much bigger if it was further way. similar to the phoenix lights. i just found that real quick as an example. but the oval shape was more pronounced. the ring or halo of lights were almost tilted on and angle. the lights lit up in a row. slowly around the oval and sped up quicker and quicker until it vanished completely without a trace. the reason why i decided to write about this now is because i was driving past that field the other day and realized you can see stars everywhere in the sky, except for where those lights were above the base.
content.summary: Above lakehurst base. bigger than a football field. 12 or more lights lit up in a row in oval/disk shape on and angle, began to light up quicker and disappeared. was like a halo of lights .

content.detailedDescription:
I was on the phone(landline) talking to my mother,when i noticed lots of movement in the sky in front of sandia mountain. at first i thought it might be birds, but on closer inspection,the images were metallic and pulsated.I grabbed my cell phone and began shooting digital video of the event. there were at least 50 of the objects...Some were together in groups, some were on their own.
during the event,i was trying to process what i was seeing.It was clear that  they weren't birds and anything that i could identify or understand.
some were stationary in clusters, others moving in different directions, they went up, down,sideways and in circles.
i believe that what i witnessed were unidentified flying objects.
i knew that planes don't travel in packs and move that fast, while changing direction.
they just disappeared from view.
it appeared they went behind the mountain, away from my view.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Approximately 50 discs assembling, in formation in front of the mountain

content.detailedDescription: 1.Sitting outside garage facing east.   2.Bright blue ball 50'diameter coming straight at me.        3.No reference complete unknown. unless you think of the incredible hulk pumped up.                     4.From east at end of 10 acre field object came out of trees, swooped down a few feet from ground .At 50 yards giant ball shot straight up and disappeared. the ball looked like a man with a huge head and shoulders. their was a crackling noise. the colors were very bright and variable. the velocity was moderate then slow until it ascended like warp drive.  5. beautiful lights unimaginable flight characteristics, seemed to be very personal because the flying humanoid giant was watching me and came very close. felt at peace and very lucky then very happy. 6. sphere made 90 degree impossible ascent at light speed in crisp blue light.  felt  safe and normal, no reason to be frightened  or worry about anything that is in complete control it is either good or bad must have been good because just gave me a good experience.
content.summary: Flew straight towards me from east, over tree tops swooped very near ground and at about 50 yards object shot straight up constantly changing colors.

content.summary: We were flying out of guadalara mexico and my sons girlfriend decided to take pictures out the window she saw what was flying outside
